## CROSS-POLLINATION RULES
Every session, agents share intel in this direction:
- CIPHER whale/founder intel → PHANTOM conviction score upgrade
- ORACLE macro read → HYDRA position sizing (reduce leverage in headwind)
- NEXUS sector rotation signal → CIPHER entry timing (wait for rotation to confirm)
- PHANTOM pattern breakout → HYDRA checks funding/OI for confluence
- HYDRA funding squeeze signal → NEXUS checks sector for cascade risk

